snippet.title: The First Descendant - Xbox Extended Gameplay First Look
snippet.description:
The First Descendant, a next-generation third-person looter shooter, 
revealed a never-before-seen Xbox Series X gameplay and announced a Crossplay Beta. 

Join the Crossplay Beta from August 22 - 28!
